                    "from": "contact@balinaisa.com",
                    "replyTo": "contact@balinaisa.com",
                    "senderName": "Balinaisa",
                    "subject": "Votre simulation Balinaisa — {{step_2['product']}} ×{{step_2['qty']}}",
                    "body_type": "html",
                    "body": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><body style=\"font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; background: #F3EFE9; padding: 32px; margin: 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\">\n\n    <div style=\"background: #8B6B45; padding: 24px 32px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff;\">Balinaisa</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"padding: 36px 32px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1714; font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\">Merci, {{trigger['body']['name']}} !</p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 28px; font-size: 15px; color: #6B6058; line-height: 1.7;\">Nous avons bien reçu votre demande de devis. Notre équipe vous contacte sous <strong>24h</strong> pour vous accompagner dans votre projet.</p>\n\n      <!-- Récap simulation -->\n      <div style=\"background: #FAF8F5; border-left: 3px solid #C4975A; border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #9E9188; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;\">Récapitulatif de votre simulation</p>\n        <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B6058; width: 50%;\">Meuble sélectionné</td>\n            <td style=\"padding: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1714;\">{{step_2['product']}} (teck massif)</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B6058;\">Quantité</td>\n            <td style=\"padding: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1714;\">{{step_2['qty']}}</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr style=\"border-top: 1px solid #E4DDD3;\">\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 0 5px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1714;\">Estimation TTC</td>\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 0 5px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #8B6B45;\">{{step_2['total_ttc']}}</td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 14px; color: #6B6058; line-height: 1.7;\">Vous pouvez également nous joindre directement :</p>\n      <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 32px;\">\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B6058;\">📧</td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"mailto:contact@balinaisa.com\" style=\"color: #8B6B45; text-decoration: none;\">contact@balinaisa.com</a></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B6058;\">📞</td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1A1714;\">07 45 06 52 16</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B6058;\">📍</td>\n          <td style=\"padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1A1714;\">370 Av. de l'Aérodrome, 33260 La Teste-de-Buch</td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <a href=\"https://balinaisa.com\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: #8B6B45; color: #ffffff; padding: 13px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;\">Découvrir notre catalogue →</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"background: #FAF8F5; padding: 14px 32px; border-top: 1px solid #E4DDD3;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9E9188;\">© 2026 Balinaisa · La Teste-de-Buch · Mobilier en teck massif artisanal</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body></html>",
                    "attachments": [],
                    "customHeaders": {}
                  },
